00:17:54,859 --> 00:17:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] Koja božanska osoba?

623
00:17:55,980 --> 00:17:57,119
[SPEAKER_01] Bog otac.

624
00:17:57,119 --> 00:17:58,160
[SPEAKER_01] Evo je važno.

625
00:17:58,160 --> 00:17:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je fakt sad jako važno.

626
00:17:59,940 --> 00:18:00,900
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

627
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] meni ovo uduševilo sad.

628
00:18:06,460 --> 00:18:07,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ja pokušavam vas zagrijati.

629
00:18:07,759 --> 00:18:08,759
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

630
00:18:08,759 --> 00:18:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] ok, ok.

631
00:18:09,460 --> 00:18:11,180
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

632
00:18:11,180 --> 00:18:13,440
[SPEAKER_01] karizme su trojstvene.

633
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ako nisu trojstveno obojane,

634
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:17,400
[SPEAKER_01] ostaju samo fenomen.

635
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:19,819
[SPEAKER_01] I onda će ostati dalje samo predrasude.

636
00:18:19,819 --> 00:18:21,519
[SPEAKER_01] I ako hjerarhija

637
00:18:21,519 --> 00:18:23,240
[SPEAKER_01] nije trojstveno obojena,

638
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:25,099
[SPEAKER_01] dar službe djelovanja,

639
00:18:25,099 --> 00:18:27,700
[SPEAKER_01] ostaje kruta institucija hjerarhija.

640
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:29,980
[SPEAKER_01] I uvijeti kako se to rješava.

641
00:18:29,980 --> 00:18:30,420
[SPEAKER_01] I što to je?

642
00:18:30,420 --> 00:18:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] Daću konkretne primjere.

643
00:18:31,900 --> 00:18:33,960
[SPEAKER_01] Vama poznati darovi,

644
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:35,140
[SPEAKER_01] vama poznati karizme.

645
00:18:35,140 --> 00:18:37,259
[SPEAKER_01] Vidjet ćemo koja je evolucija.

646
00:18:37,259 --> 00:18:38,279
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

647
00:18:38,279 --> 00:18:40,779
[SPEAKER_01] crkveni oci ove tri stvari

648
00:18:40,779 --> 00:18:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] zovu pneumatika.

649
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:44,339
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo malo vulkanizeri,

650
00:18:44,339 --> 00:18:44,680
[SPEAKER_01] ali eto.

651
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, pneumatika.

652
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:47,839
[SPEAKER_01] Što spada u pneumatiku?

653
00:18:47,839 --> 00:18:48,859
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

654
00:18:48,859 --> 00:18:50,720
[SPEAKER_01] različiti dar i isti duh.

655
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:52,740
[SPEAKER_01] Harismata ili karizmata.

656
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:53,420
[SPEAKER_01] Kako želite,

657
00:18:53,420 --> 00:18:54,420
[SPEAKER_01] kako vi će izgovarati,

658
00:18:54,420 --> 00:18:55,799
[SPEAKER_01] jako je pravilni je harismata.

659
00:18:55,799 --> 00:18:56,400
[SPEAKER_01] haris.

660
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:57,579
[SPEAKER_01] Nije karis,

661
00:18:57,579 --> 00:18:58,380
[SPEAKER_01] nego haris.

662
00:18:58,380 --> 00:19:00,140
[SPEAKER_01] Grčki je takav.

663
00:19:00,140 --> 00:19:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] Hi je,

664
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] nije kapa.

665
00:19:01,099 --> 00:19:02,140
[SPEAKER_01] Hi,

666
00:19:02,140 --> 00:19:02,880
[SPEAKER_01] nije kapa.

667
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:03,160
[SPEAKER_01] Ok?

668
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,279
[SPEAKER_01] To su slova.

669
00:19:04,279 --> 00:19:05,039
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

670
00:19:05,039 --> 00:19:05,660
[SPEAKER_01] harismata.

671
00:19:05,660 --> 00:19:06,019
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo,

672
00:19:06,019 --> 00:19:07,160
[SPEAKER_01] različiti dar i isti duh.

673
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,019
[SPEAKER_01] To je harismata.

674
00:19:08,019 --> 00:19:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] To su karizme.

675
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:10,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo što mi zovemo karizme.

676
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ok?

677
00:19:11,119 --> 00:19:12,740
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo,

678
00:19:12,740 --> 00:19:14,279
[SPEAKER_01] različite službe,

679
00:19:14,279 --> 00:19:15,460
[SPEAKER_01] isti gospodin.

680
00:19:15,460 --> 00:19:16,579
[SPEAKER_01] Diakonija.

681
00:19:16,579 --> 00:19:18,140
[SPEAKER_01] Dunosni džakon,

682
00:19:18,140 --> 00:19:19,140
[SPEAKER_01] onaj koji poslužuje.

683
00:19:19,140 --> 00:19:20,720
[SPEAKER_01] Diakonija znači služiti.

684
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:21,759
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

685
00:19:21,759 --> 00:19:22,519
[SPEAKER_01] uzor je krist.

686
00:19:22,519 --> 00:19:23,880
[SPEAKER_01] U prvom je uzor duh sveti,

687
00:19:25,799 --> 00:19:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] nakon toga idu službe.

688
00:19:27,519 --> 00:19:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] Uzor je krist,

689
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:30,480
[SPEAKER_01] on je taj koji je poslužitelj,

690
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:31,720
[SPEAKER_01] sjetite se sami,

691
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,319
[SPEAKER_01] koji je sluga.

692
00:19:32,319 --> 00:19:34,359
[SPEAKER_01] I djelovanja,

693
00:19:34,359 --> 00:19:35,519
[SPEAKER_01] energomata.

694
00:19:35,519 --> 00:19:36,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ok?

695
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:37,119
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

696
00:19:37,119 --> 00:19:38,380
[SPEAKER_01] to je konačno.

697
00:19:38,380 --> 00:19:40,160
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo sada vidjeti

698
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:40,759
[SPEAKER_01] kako on,

699
00:19:40,759 --> 00:19:41,119
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

700
00:19:41,119 --> 00:19:41,660
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje,

701
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:43,640
[SPEAKER_01] koje on ovdje darove nabraja.

702
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:44,980
[SPEAKER_01] I to su darovi prve crkve.

703
00:19:44,980 --> 00:19:46,019
[SPEAKER_01] I vidjet ćemo

704
00:19:46,019 --> 00:19:49,400
[SPEAKER_01] kako ih staviti upravo kroz ovo.

705
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:51,359
[SPEAKER_01] Vidjet ćemo koliko je darova

706
00:19:51,359 --> 00:19:53,160
[SPEAKER_01] i kako ih on provlači

707
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,740
[SPEAKER_01] od harizmata

708
00:19:54,740 --> 00:19:55,779
[SPEAKER_01] preko diakonija

709
00:19:55,779 --> 00:19:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] do energomata.

710
00:19:56,960 --> 00:19:57,940
[SPEAKER_01] Morate shvatiti

711
00:19:57,940 --> 00:19:58,599
[SPEAKER_01] da je sveti red

712
00:19:58,599 --> 00:19:59,559
[SPEAKER_01] tako koncipiran.

713
00:19:59,559 --> 00:20:00,640
[SPEAKER_01] Vi znate koji su supnjevi

714
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] svetoga reda.

715
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,599
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

716
00:20:02,599 --> 00:20:04,400
[SPEAKER_01] zanimarite svečaništvo,

717
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,200
[SPEAKER_01] svečaništva nije bilo

718
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:05,900
[SPEAKER_01] u prvoj crkvi.

719
00:20:05,900 --> 00:20:06,680
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

720
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:08,380
[SPEAKER_01] džakon i biskup.

721
00:20:08,380 --> 00:20:10,859
[SPEAKER_01] Biskup kao nasljedovatelj

722
00:20:10,859 --> 00:20:12,420
[SPEAKER_01] apostola.

723
00:20:12,420 --> 00:20:12,759
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

724
00:20:12,759 --> 00:20:13,700
[SPEAKER_01] svečanika još nije bilo

725
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:14,259
[SPEAKER_01] u to vrijeme.

726
00:20:14,259 --> 00:20:15,319
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

727
00:20:15,319 --> 00:20:16,039
[SPEAKER_01] i džakon je taj

728
00:20:16,039 --> 00:20:17,160
[SPEAKER_01] koji poslužuje biskupa.

729
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Džakon.

730
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:19,799
[SPEAKER_01] Džakon je biskupsko vezan

731
00:20:19,799 --> 00:20:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] uz oltar.

732
00:20:20,460 --> 00:20:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

733
00:20:21,099 --> 00:20:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] imate karizmu.

734
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:23,700
[SPEAKER_01] Karizma je poziv.

735
00:20:23,700 --> 00:20:24,519
[SPEAKER_01] Duhovni poziv.

736
00:20:24,519 --> 00:20:25,359
[SPEAKER_01] To je karizma.

737
00:20:25,359 --> 00:20:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga

738
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] može ostati samo karizma.

739
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:29,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ja osjećam poziv,

740
00:20:29,799 --> 00:20:30,720
[SPEAKER_01] meni je Bog progovorio.

741
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] I možeš ostati samo na tome.

742
00:20:31,900 --> 00:20:32,839
[SPEAKER_01] I to je tvoje.

743
00:20:32,839 --> 00:20:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga

744
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,240
[SPEAKER_01] možeš ići dalje.

745
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:37,200
[SPEAKER_01] Diakonija,

746
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,680
[SPEAKER_01] znači posluživanje,

747
00:20:38,680 --> 00:20:39,259
[SPEAKER_01] služenje.

748
00:20:39,259 --> 00:20:40,640
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je džakon.

749
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:42,200
[SPEAKER_01] I energomata,

750
00:20:42,200 --> 00:20:42,859
[SPEAKER_01] djelovanje,

751
00:20:42,859 --> 00:20:43,559
[SPEAKER_01] biskup.

752
00:20:43,559 --> 00:20:44,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je samo

753
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:46,279
[SPEAKER_01] plastičan primjer.

754
00:20:46,279 --> 00:20:48,240
[SPEAKER_01] Jel vidite konkretno još neke darove.

755
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:50,259
[SPEAKER_01] Jel ste shvatili ovo tri?

756
00:20:50,259 --> 00:20:51,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je vrlo važno.

757
00:20:51,359 --> 00:20:52,240
[SPEAKER_01] Ok.

758
00:20:52,240 --> 00:20:54,220
[SPEAKER_01] Sada kaže onda braja darove.

759
00:20:54,220 --> 00:20:55,380
[SPEAKER_01] Jel vidite koji su darovi.

760
00:20:55,380 --> 00:20:57,440
[SPEAKER_01] Jel vidite koliko ih je.

761
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] Znate da su brojke bitne u Bibliji.

762
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:00,339
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

763
00:21:00,339 --> 00:21:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] doista,

764
00:21:01,420 --> 00:21:03,720
[SPEAKER_01] jednomu se po duhu daje

765
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:04,940
[SPEAKER_01] riječ mudrosti,

766
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:06,900
[SPEAKER_01] drugomu riječ spoznanja,

767
00:21:06,900 --> 00:21:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] po tom istom duhu.

768
00:21:08,599 --> 00:21:10,519
[SPEAKER_01] drugomu vjera u tom istom duhu.

769
00:21:10,519 --> 00:21:13,140
[SPEAKER_01] Drugomu dar i liječenja u tom jednom duhu.

770
00:21:13,140 --> 00:21:14,799
[SPEAKER_01] Drugomu čudotvorstva,

771
00:21:14,799 --> 00:21:16,720
[SPEAKER_01] drugomu prorokovanje,

772
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:18,480
[SPEAKER_01] drugomu različivanje duhova,

773
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:20,400
[SPEAKER_01] drugom je različiti jezici

774
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:22,099
[SPEAKER_01] i drugom je tumačenje jezika.

775
00:21:22,099 --> 00:21:22,819
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko ih je?

776
00:21:22,819 --> 00:21:23,980
[SPEAKER_01] Devet.

777
00:21:23,980 --> 00:21:24,759
[SPEAKER_01] Pa naravno, da.

778
00:21:24,759 --> 00:21:28,740
[SPEAKER_01] Brojka devet je biblijski broj neba.

779
00:21:28,740 --> 00:21:30,160
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, upravo po tim darovima

780
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:33,200
[SPEAKER_01] treba ostvariti kraljstvo Božje na zemlji.

781
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo sad vidjeti

782
00:21:35,079 --> 00:21:36,319
[SPEAKER_01] kako, dakle,

783
00:21:36,319 --> 00:21:38,559
[SPEAKER_01] nakon toga ide ona palova usporedba

784
00:21:38,559 --> 00:21:40,700
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, crkve s tijelom,

785
00:21:40,700 --> 00:21:42,819
[SPEAKER_01] idemo vidjeti sada konkretno,

786
00:21:42,819 --> 00:21:44,700
[SPEAKER_01] evo, na ovim temeljnim

787
00:21:44,700 --> 00:21:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] darovima, karizmama,

788
00:21:46,579 --> 00:21:48,559
[SPEAKER_01] biblijskim, a onda i prve crkve,

789
00:21:48,559 --> 00:21:49,779
[SPEAKER_01] jer riječ je o prvoj crkvi,

790
00:21:49,779 --> 00:21:52,940
[SPEAKER_01] vidjeti kako

791
00:21:52,940 --> 00:21:55,900
[SPEAKER_01] se provlači određeni dar,

792
00:21:55,900 --> 00:21:58,319
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, od karizme,

793
00:21:58,319 --> 00:22:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] zatim diakonija

794
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:01,220
[SPEAKER_01] i onda energomata.

795
00:22:01,220 --> 00:22:02,480
[SPEAKER_01] Vi morate znati jednu stvar.

796
00:22:02,880 --> 00:22:03,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ova podjela kroz

797
00:22:03,940 --> 00:22:06,079
[SPEAKER_01] božanske osobe

798
00:22:06,079 --> 00:22:07,420
[SPEAKER_01] ne znači

799
00:22:07,420 --> 00:22:08,579
[SPEAKER_01] i ne bi smjelo,

800
00:22:08,579 --> 00:22:09,980
[SPEAKER_01] jer onda imate problema

801
00:22:09,980 --> 00:22:11,519
[SPEAKER_01] sa shvaćanjem presvetog trojstva,

802
00:22:11,519 --> 00:22:13,400
[SPEAKER_01] da je sad karizma manje

803
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:14,480
[SPEAKER_01] od energomata,

804
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:14,920
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

805
00:22:14,920 --> 00:22:16,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ili, ne znam,

806
00:22:16,420 --> 00:22:18,859
[SPEAKER_01] energometa je veće od samo onog,

807
00:22:18,859 --> 00:22:20,200
[SPEAKER_01] to nisu stupnjevi,

808
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:21,440
[SPEAKER_01] to nisu stupnjevi.

809
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:22,880
[SPEAKER_01] Energomata,

810
00:22:22,880 --> 00:22:24,299
[SPEAKER_01] znači ovo djelovanje,

811
00:22:24,299 --> 00:22:26,599
[SPEAKER_01] predpostavlja već neku karizmu,

812
00:22:26,599 --> 00:22:27,440
[SPEAKER_01] da imaš karizmu.

813
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:28,660
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, čim?

814
00:22:28,660 --> 00:22:31,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, svaki biskup je karizmatičan,

815
00:22:31,119 --> 00:22:32,559
[SPEAKER_01] jer ne može doći do energomata

816
00:22:32,559 --> 00:22:33,420
[SPEAKER_01] ako nema.

817
00:22:33,420 --> 00:22:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] Samo on je,

818
00:22:34,019 --> 00:22:35,700
[SPEAKER_01] postoje neki koji su svoju

819
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] ili nisu svjesni svoje karizmatičnosti

820
00:22:38,539 --> 00:22:39,660
[SPEAKER_01] ili, dakle,

821
00:22:39,660 --> 00:22:41,039
[SPEAKER_01] su jednostavno zatomili.

822
00:22:41,039 --> 00:22:42,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ali karizma postoji.

823
00:22:42,619 --> 00:22:43,900
[SPEAKER_01] Postoji dar duha svetog.

824
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:45,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znači on da bi postao biskup.

825
00:22:45,059 --> 00:22:46,420
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, vidjet ćemo

826
00:22:46,420 --> 00:22:47,720
[SPEAKER_01] što se zapravo konkretno je.

827
00:22:48,180 --> 00:22:50,059
[SPEAKER_01] i naravno, vidjet ćemo kroz različite darove

828
00:22:50,059 --> 00:22:50,720
[SPEAKER_01] koje imate,

829
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:52,480
[SPEAKER_01] kako možemo razlikovati

830
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:54,059
[SPEAKER_01] karizmatičnog,

831
00:22:54,059 --> 00:22:55,740
[SPEAKER_01] ministranta, čitača,

832
00:22:55,740 --> 00:22:56,759
[SPEAKER_01] to su isto sve karizme,

833
00:22:56,759 --> 00:22:58,619
[SPEAKER_01] svečenika, biskupa,

834
00:22:58,619 --> 00:22:59,839
[SPEAKER_01] sakristana, zvonara,

835
00:22:59,839 --> 00:23:01,720
[SPEAKER_01] od onog, ajmo reći, profesionalnog.

836
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vidjet ćemo kako u poslanici,

837
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] druge poslanici,

838
00:23:04,619 --> 00:23:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] Timote i u Pavo,

