[SPEAKER_01] E to je problem.

1056
00:28:15,460 --> 00:28:17,279
[SPEAKER_01] Što kod karizmatika

1057
00:28:17,279 --> 00:28:18,579
[SPEAKER_01] harismata

1058
00:28:18,579 --> 00:28:19,279
