1059
00:28:19,279 --> 00:28:21,279
[SPEAKER_01] i ne ide na diakonija

1060
00:28:21,279 --> 00:28:22,980
[SPEAKER_01] i na energomata.

1061
00:28:22,980 --> 00:28:23,779
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo dalje.

1062
00:28:23,779 --> 00:28:24,839
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo sad vidjeti

1063
00:28:24,839 --> 00:28:26,440
[SPEAKER_01] u srednjem vijeku

1064
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:30,720
[SPEAKER_01] koje su nove karizme došle

1065
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:32,400
[SPEAKER_01] i kako se one provlače kroz ovo.

1066
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:34,519
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to je nešto što smo i danas naslijedili.

1067
00:28:34,519 --> 00:28:36,140
[SPEAKER_01] Tu dolazi svećeništvo.

1068
00:28:36,140 --> 00:28:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] Svećeništvo je bilo i u ranijoj crkvi,

1069
00:28:40,579 --> 00:28:42,059
[SPEAKER_01] nije baš došlo sa srednjim vijekom.

1070
00:28:42,059 --> 00:28:42,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ali,

1071
00:28:42,819 --> 00:28:44,819
[SPEAKER_01] ideče, pitanje celibata,

1072
00:28:44,819 --> 00:28:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne mogu imašnjavati celibat nekome

1073
00:28:47,039 --> 00:28:48,400
[SPEAKER_01] koji će se samo s time sprnat.

1074
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:50,099
[SPEAKER_01] I bilo u crkvi, bilo izvan.

1075
00:28:50,099 --> 00:28:51,039
[SPEAKER_01] Jer, fakat, ono,

1076
00:28:51,039 --> 00:28:52,680
[SPEAKER_01] trebaš vremena da uopće objasniš

1077
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:54,579
[SPEAKER_01] nekome, da uopće shvati kontekst svega

1078
00:28:54,579 --> 00:28:55,220
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

1079
00:28:55,220 --> 00:28:56,599
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, nekaj smo prvo su bili

1080
00:28:56,599 --> 00:28:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] džakon i biskup.

1081
00:28:57,460 --> 00:28:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] Svećenika nije bilo.

1082
00:28:58,500 --> 00:28:59,799
[SPEAKER_01] Jer svećeništvo, nešto je vezano

1083
00:28:59,799 --> 00:29:00,740
[SPEAKER_01] u spogaštinu

1084
00:29:00,740 --> 00:29:02,160
[SPEAKER_01] i u židovsku religiju.

1085
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,480
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo su bili svećenici,

1086
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:04,720
[SPEAKER_01] svećenice i tako dalje.

1087
00:29:04,819 --> 00:29:05,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ta riječ svećenik, jel?

1088
00:29:05,900 --> 00:29:07,740
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim,

1089
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:10,099
[SPEAKER_01] kako je crkva postala sve veća, veća i veća,

1090
00:29:10,099 --> 00:29:12,700
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, biskup je trebao,

1091
00:29:12,700 --> 00:29:13,420
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći,

1092
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:16,339
[SPEAKER_01] svog nekog zamjednika.

1093
00:29:16,339 --> 00:29:17,160
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo reći,

1094
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:19,180
[SPEAKER_01] svećenici su kapelani biskupima.

1095
00:29:19,180 --> 00:29:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo to tako reći.

1096
00:29:21,099 --> 00:29:21,640
[SPEAKER_01] I onda,

1097
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] ovo što je Mojsije napravio,

1098
00:29:23,539 --> 00:29:24,559
[SPEAKER_01] starješine.

1099
00:29:24,559 --> 00:29:26,599
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, voditelji općina,

1100
00:29:26,599 --> 00:29:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] nešto bi danas gospodin Pavlić

1101
00:29:29,500 --> 00:29:31,079
[SPEAKER_01] ili gospodin Stašević možda bili,

1102
00:29:31,079 --> 00:29:33,160
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje u Botincu.

1103
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:34,640
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, prezbiterost,

1104
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:35,039
[SPEAKER_01] to znači,

1105
00:29:35,039 --> 00:29:35,839
[SPEAKER_01] čuli za tu riječ,

1106
00:29:35,839 --> 00:29:36,299
[SPEAKER_01] prezbiterost,

1107
00:29:36,299 --> 00:29:37,180
[SPEAKER_01] znači starješina,

1108
00:29:37,180 --> 00:29:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] koji je bio voditelj neke općine,

1109
00:29:38,539 --> 00:29:39,380
[SPEAKER_01] mjesne zajednice,

1110
00:29:39,380 --> 00:29:40,160
[SPEAKER_01] mjesnog odbora.

1111
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1112
00:29:40,880 --> 00:29:41,460
[SPEAKER_01] oni su,

1113
00:29:41,460 --> 00:29:44,160
[SPEAKER_01] na njih su se položilo ruke

1114
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:46,160
[SPEAKER_01] i oni su postali posvećene osobe

1115
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] i zato u početku,

1116
00:29:47,039 --> 00:29:47,579
[SPEAKER_01] kad kažu,

1117
00:29:47,579 --> 00:29:49,259
[SPEAKER_01] pa nije bilo svećničko celibato

1118
00:29:49,259 --> 00:29:49,660
[SPEAKER_01] od početka,

1119
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:50,900
[SPEAKER_01] onda nije kad su bili starješine

1120
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:52,359
