1121
00:29:52,359 --> 00:29:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1122
00:29:52,539 --> 00:29:54,339
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo u tom trenutku tada danu.

1123
00:29:54,339 --> 00:29:55,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kasnije,

1124
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:58,140
[SPEAKER_01] sa umiranjem tih starješina,

1125
00:29:58,140 --> 00:29:59,160
[SPEAKER_01] generacije starješina

1126
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,680
[SPEAKER_01] koji su postali svećenici,

1127
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:01,500
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1128
