[SPEAKER_01] dolazi do karizme neženstva,

1129
00:30:04,140 --> 00:30:04,799
[SPEAKER_01] beženstva,

1130
00:30:04,799 --> 00:30:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] djevičanstva i tako dalje.

1131
00:30:06,099 --> 00:30:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] Sada imate,

1132
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:07,359
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1133
00:30:07,359 --> 00:30:12,440
[SPEAKER_01] nešto što je duhovno možda jako bitno.

1134
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] Baš ovako,

1135
00:30:13,380 --> 00:30:14,700
[SPEAKER_01] ovo sve je duhovno bitno,

1136
00:30:14,700 --> 00:30:15,819
[SPEAKER_01] ali ovo je još duhovnije,

1137
00:30:15,819 --> 00:30:16,680
[SPEAKER_01] ja vam to tako reći.

1138
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:17,779
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1139
00:30:17,779 --> 00:30:18,359
[SPEAKER_01] a to je ovo.

1140
00:30:18,359 --> 00:30:20,099
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1141
00:30:20,099 --> 00:30:21,319
[SPEAKER_01] da se harismata,

1142
