[SPEAKER_01] u to ulazi.

1149
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:29,319
[SPEAKER_01] Neženstvo,

1150
00:30:29,319 --> 00:30:30,299
[SPEAKER_01] djevičanstvo,

1151
00:30:30,299 --> 00:30:31,559
[SPEAKER_01] siromaštvo,

1152
00:30:31,559 --> 00:30:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] poslušnost,

1153
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:34,099
[SPEAKER_01] poslušnost,

1154
00:30:34,099 --> 00:30:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1155
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:35,720
[SPEAKER_01] vjernost,

1156
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:36,799
[SPEAKER_01] bilo koji način,

1157
00:30:36,799 --> 00:30:37,180
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1158
