[SPEAKER_01] jel?

1168
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:45,680
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1169
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:46,359
[SPEAKER_01] siromaštvo,

1170
00:30:46,359 --> 00:30:47,279
[SPEAKER_01] poslušnost,

1171
00:30:47,279 --> 00:30:48,759
[SPEAKER_01] to je sve karizma.

1172
00:30:48,759 --> 00:30:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] Služenje,

1173
00:30:50,460 --> 00:30:52,880
[SPEAKER_01] diakonija tih stvari,

1174
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:55,720
[SPEAKER_01] je zagovaranje i dijela milosrđa.

1175
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:57,119
[SPEAKER_01] Zagovaranje.

1176
00:30:57,119 --> 00:30:57,380
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1177
00:30:57,380 --> 00:30:57,799
[SPEAKER_01] Svijete se,

1178
00:30:57,799 --> 00:30:58,200
[SPEAKER_01] monaški,

1179
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:59,680
[SPEAKER_01] asketski redovi i tako dalje,

1180
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:00,940
[SPEAKER_01] su zagovaratelji.

1181
00:31:00,940 --> 00:31:01,180
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1182
00:31:01,180 --> 00:31:01,700
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1183
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:02,859
[SPEAKER_01] prikazuju sami sebe,

1184
00:31:02,859 --> 00:31:03,579
[SPEAKER_01] i oni koji žive,

1185
00:31:03,579 --> 00:31:04,140
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1186
00:31:04,140 --> 00:31:04,720
[SPEAKER_01] u celibatu,

1187
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:07,579
