1188
00:31:07,579 --> 00:31:08,599
[SPEAKER_01] kojim su poslali.

1189
00:31:08,599 --> 00:31:10,599
[SPEAKER_01] A što je energobata?

1190
00:31:13,259 --> 00:31:14,579
