1191
00:31:14,579 --> 00:31:16,240
[SPEAKER_01] E sad,

1192
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:17,140
[SPEAKER_01] pogledajte sad,

1193
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:19,160
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje se zapravo može najbolje vidjeti,

1194
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] tu sam htio ostaviti ovaj primjer,

1195
00:31:20,539 --> 00:31:20,900
[SPEAKER_01] baš,

1196
00:31:20,900 --> 00:31:22,579
[SPEAKER_01] da pokažem što se događa

1197
00:31:22,579 --> 00:31:25,119
[SPEAKER_01] kada imaš energobata,

1198
00:31:25,119 --> 00:31:25,720
