1210
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:46,980
[SPEAKER_01] Jel nije?

1211
00:31:46,980 --> 00:31:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Što je,

1212
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] na primjer,

1213
00:31:51,559 --> 00:31:53,660
[SPEAKER_01] sad ću reći,

1214
00:31:53,660 --> 00:31:55,180
[SPEAKER_01] naučavanje,

1215
00:31:55,180 --> 00:31:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] katehiziranje bez harismata,

1216
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,059
[SPEAKER_01] riječ mudrosti.

1217
00:31:58,059 --> 00:31:59,559
[SPEAKER_01] Što je to?

1218
00:31:59,559 --> 00:32:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] Praviti se pamet,

1219
00:32:01,579 --> 00:32:02,700
[SPEAKER_01] dosadno, da, možda je to.

1220
00:32:02,700 --> 00:32:04,759
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1221
00:32:04,759 --> 00:32:06,799
[SPEAKER_01] I s druge strane,

1222
00:32:06,799 --> 00:32:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] iz druge strane,

1223
00:32:08,079 --> 00:32:09,180
[SPEAKER_01] obrnuću,

1224
00:32:09,180 --> 00:32:09,700
[SPEAKER_01] obrnuću,

1225
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:10,359
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći,

1226
00:32:10,359 --> 00:32:11,299
[SPEAKER_01] oštricu,

1227
00:32:11,980 --> 00:32:12,940
[SPEAKER_01] što je neženstvo,

1228
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:13,700
[SPEAKER_01] djevičanstvo,

1229
00:32:13,700 --> 00:32:15,579
[SPEAKER_01] celibat i poslušnost,

1230
00:32:15,579 --> 00:32:16,420
[SPEAKER_01] bez,

1231
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] ako nije usmjereno,

1232
00:32:18,019 --> 00:32:19,740
[SPEAKER_01] prea mučaništvu.

1233
00:32:19,740 --> 00:32:20,519
[SPEAKER_01] Mi znamo,

1234
00:32:20,519 --> 00:32:21,359
[SPEAKER_01] da nisu svi,

1235
00:32:21,359 --> 00:32:22,019
[SPEAKER_01] koji su,

1236
00:32:22,019 --> 00:32:23,200
[SPEAKER_01] sveci i tako dalje,

1237
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:25,039
[SPEAKER_01] koji su živjeli tako,

1238
00:32:25,039 --> 00:32:27,299
[SPEAKER_01] automatski doživjeli mučaništvo.

1239
00:32:27,299 --> 00:32:27,660
[SPEAKER_01] Ali,

1240
