[SPEAKER_01] jer su spremili svoju dušu.

1242
00:32:31,079 --> 00:32:32,400
[SPEAKER_01] Svijetite se koliko su molili,

1243
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:33,059
[SPEAKER_01] daj da budem,

1244
00:32:33,059 --> 00:32:33,339
[SPEAKER_01] recimo,

1245
00:32:33,339 --> 00:32:34,380
[SPEAKER_01] mala Terezija,

1246
00:32:34,380 --> 00:32:35,400
[SPEAKER_01] Sveti Franjo,

1247
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje,

1248
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,099
[SPEAKER_01] daj da budem tvoj mučanik.

1249
00:32:37,099 --> 00:32:37,480
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno,

1250
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:38,440
[SPEAKER_01] bila je ta spremnost,

1251
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:39,799
[SPEAKER_01] da je bilo u kojem trenutku,

1252
00:32:39,799 --> 00:32:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] neko,

1253
00:32:40,079 --> 00:32:40,720
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je znao,

1254
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:41,500
[SPEAKER_01] bilo u kojem trenutku,

1255
00:32:41,500 --> 00:32:42,380
