1479
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:40,440
[SPEAKER_01] samo pročišćenje.

1480
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:44,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što bi isto htio,

1481
00:37:44,679 --> 00:37:45,480
[SPEAKER_01] svakako,

1482
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:47,619
[SPEAKER_01] u ovom sveu,

1483
00:37:47,619 --> 00:37:48,199
[SPEAKER_01] mi znamo.

1484
00:37:48,199 --> 00:37:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] Mi cijelo vrijeme govorimo o tome

1485
00:37:49,519 --> 00:37:51,500
[SPEAKER_01] i znamo da su sve karizme važne.

1486
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pavao će reći da je,

1487
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:54,760
[SPEAKER_01] kada uspoređuje,

1488
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:55,460
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1489
00:37:55,460 --> 00:37:56,900
[SPEAKER_01] govor jezicima o prorokovanju,

1490
00:37:56,900 --> 00:37:57,119
[SPEAKER_01] da je,

1491
00:37:57,119 --> 00:37:59,039
[SPEAKER_01] tu je jedni put kad Pavao daje

1492
00:37:59,039 --> 00:38:00,179
[SPEAKER_01] nekoj karizmi prednost,

1493
00:38:00,179 --> 00:38:02,679
[SPEAKER_01] prorokovanju je dao prednost pred,

1494
00:38:02,679 --> 00:38:03,139
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1495
00:38:03,139 --> 00:38:04,440
[SPEAKER_01] jezicima,

1496
00:38:04,440 --> 00:38:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno govoru jezicima.

1497
00:38:06,119 --> 00:38:07,760
[SPEAKER_01] E sad,

1498
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:09,199
[SPEAKER_01] objasnio sam polaganje ruku,

1499
00:38:09,199 --> 00:38:09,860
[SPEAKER_01] međutim,

1500
00:38:09,860 --> 00:38:11,280
[SPEAKER_01] što je sa počivanjem u duhu?

1501
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] Počivanje u duhu nije karizma,

1502
00:38:13,579 --> 00:38:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] ali je u,

1503
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:15,619
[SPEAKER_01] dajmo reći,

1504
00:38:15,619 --> 00:38:16,780
[SPEAKER_01] karizmaskom sustavu.

1505
00:38:17,239 --> 00:38:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Počivanje u duhu je zapravo

1506
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:20,780
[SPEAKER_01] početak za otvorenost

1507
00:38:20,780 --> 00:38:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] prema nekom mističnom fenomenu.

1508
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:23,719
[SPEAKER_01] A vi znate kad smo radili,

1509
00:38:23,719 --> 00:38:24,019
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1510
00:38:24,019 --> 00:38:24,900
[SPEAKER_01] mistične fenomene,

1511
00:38:24,900 --> 00:38:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] da sam dopravio razliku

1512
00:38:26,079 --> 00:38:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] mističnih fenomena,

1513
00:38:27,099 --> 00:38:28,340
[SPEAKER_01] kao što su stigme,

1514
00:38:28,340 --> 00:38:29,320
[SPEAKER_01] bilokacija,

1515
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:30,380
[SPEAKER_01] vizije,

1516
00:38:30,380 --> 00:38:31,199
[SPEAKER_01] lokucije itd.

1517
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] i karizmatskih fenomena.

1518
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1519
00:38:33,539 --> 00:38:34,519
[SPEAKER_01] počivanje u duhu

1520
00:38:34,519 --> 00:38:35,780
[SPEAKER_01] je pripremanje

1521
00:38:35,780 --> 00:38:36,840
[SPEAKER_01] vlastitoga duha

1522
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] i vlastite

1523
00:38:37,500 --> 00:38:39,179
[SPEAKER_01] unutarnje psihičke strukture

1524
00:38:39,179 --> 00:38:40,780
[SPEAKER_01] za određeni mistični fenomen,

1525
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:41,559
[SPEAKER_01] kstazu,

1526
00:38:41,559 --> 00:38:43,019
[SPEAKER_01] viziju itd.

1527
00:38:43,019 --> 00:38:43,460
[SPEAKER_01] itd.

1528
00:38:43,460 --> 00:38:44,179
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1529
00:38:44,179 --> 00:38:44,619
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći,

1530
00:38:44,619 --> 00:38:45,719
[SPEAKER_01] to je nekako na rubu

1531
00:38:45,719 --> 00:38:46,840
[SPEAKER_01] između ovih dviju stvari.

1532
00:38:46,840 --> 00:38:47,900
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1533
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:48,519
[SPEAKER_01] e sada,

1534
00:38:48,519 --> 00:38:49,260
[SPEAKER_01] idemo vidjeti,

1535
00:38:49,260 --> 00:38:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] i s time ću zaključiti,

1536
00:38:50,539 --> 00:38:51,920
[SPEAKER_01] pa su onda vaše pitanja

1537
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] na redu.

1538
00:38:52,260 --> 00:38:53,920
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1539
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] ono što mi je možda

1540
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:56,280
[SPEAKER_01] najvažnije od svega

1541
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] da ovdje večera zapamtite,

1542
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:03,639
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj hirarhijski dio

1543
00:39:03,639 --> 00:39:05,119
[SPEAKER_01] i ovaj karizmatski dio

1544
00:39:05,119 --> 00:39:06,219
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo ne mogu

1545
00:39:06,219 --> 00:39:07,099
[SPEAKER_01] jedan bez drugoga.

1546
00:39:07,099 --> 00:39:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] Baš kroz ovo stupnjevanje

1547
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:09,579
[SPEAKER_01] harizmata,

1548
00:39:09,579 --> 00:39:10,280
[SPEAKER_01] diakonija

1549
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] i energomata.

1550
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:12,760
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1551
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno problem je

1552
00:39:14,579 --> 00:39:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] što neki ostanu

1553
00:39:17,079 --> 00:39:19,099
[SPEAKER_01] zadivljeni samo jednim stupnjem.

1554
00:39:19,099 --> 00:39:20,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

1555
00:39:20,119 --> 00:39:20,719
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći,

1556
00:39:20,719 --> 00:39:22,400
[SPEAKER_01] karizmatici samo sa harizmata,

1557
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:25,340
[SPEAKER_01] a ovi koji su več na energomata,

1558
00:39:25,340 --> 00:39:27,599
[SPEAKER_01] oni samo gledaju to svoje upravljanje

1559
00:39:27,599 --> 00:39:28,360
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje,

1560
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:29,920
[SPEAKER_01] bez svijesti

1561
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:30,980
[SPEAKER_01] da je karizma

1562
00:39:30,980 --> 00:39:32,900
[SPEAKER_01] predvodila tome što danas jest.

1563
00:39:32,900 --> 00:39:37,599
[SPEAKER_01] E sada, rekao sam, a joj reći poslansnica za kraj,

1564
00:39:37,599 --> 00:39:42,239
[SPEAKER_01] kako prepoznati karizmatični ud crkve,

1565
00:39:42,239 --> 00:39:47,179
[SPEAKER_01] dakle ud član, kako prepoznati karizmatičnog člana crkve,

1566
00:39:47,179 --> 00:39:52,119
[SPEAKER_01] karizmatičnog služitelja crkve, ono koji to odrađuje.

1567
00:39:52,119 --> 00:39:56,900
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Pavao u svojoj poslanici Timoteju, druga Timoteju,

1568
00:39:57,420 --> 00:40:00,639
[SPEAKER_01] obah na početku, kada on piše, dakle, tamo Timoteju,

1569
00:40:00,639 --> 00:40:04,320
[SPEAKER_01] u kontekstu služitelja riječi, dakle, onaj koji navješta riječ,

1570
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:06,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji čita, možda joj reći, koji je tumači,

1571
00:40:06,239 --> 00:40:10,440
[SPEAKER_01] a to je nešto što crkveni oci, dakle, žele preliti

1572
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] upravo te karakteristike, upravo te Pavlove,

1573
00:40:13,039 --> 00:40:18,659
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći, kriterije da prepoznate karizmatičnog čitača,

1574
00:40:18,659 --> 00:40:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] ministranta, zvonara, sakristana, častnu, svečenika, biskupa,

1575
00:40:22,039 --> 00:40:26,380
[SPEAKER_01] kako god želite, vozača biskupa, vulkanizera biskupa,

1576
00:40:26,380 --> 00:40:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] frizera, svečenika i tako dalje, ovaj,

1577
00:40:29,340 --> 00:40:32,719
[SPEAKER_01] imam jako karizmatičnu frizerku, dakle,

1578
00:40:32,719 --> 00:40:36,019
[SPEAKER_01] vi ste po kosi, karizmatična je.

1579
00:40:36,019 --> 00:40:39,940
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, kako prepoznati? Evo, dakle, četiri su kriterija.

1580
00:40:39,940 --> 00:40:45,500
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo, životni kontekst, u Timoteju slučaju,

1581
00:40:45,500 --> 00:40:47,079
[SPEAKER_01] životni kontekst služi te ne riječi, dakle,

1582
00:40:47,079 --> 00:40:49,340
[SPEAKER_01] životni kontekst onoga koji nešto radi.

1583
00:40:49,340 --> 00:40:53,219
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, što to znači? Da, ako sam ja,

1584
00:40:53,219 --> 00:40:56,139
[SPEAKER_01] evo, daću jedan primjer. Ako sam ja, dakle, evo, ja sam svečenik.

1585
00:40:56,139 --> 00:41:00,320
[SPEAKER_01] Jesam li ja u svoj poziv stavio svoj životni kontekst?

1586
00:41:00,420 --> 00:41:04,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ili ga se odričem? Ili se stravim onoga gdje sam, ne znam,

1587
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:07,019
[SPEAKER_01] odrastao, gdje sam djelovao, što sam radio prije?

1588
00:41:07,019 --> 00:41:09,900
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to je sve nešto bilo preduvjet, jel?

1589
00:41:09,900 --> 00:41:13,059
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ajmo reći, životni kontekst ove župe.

1590
00:41:13,059 --> 00:41:15,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo reći, životni kontekst, jel?

1591
00:41:15,119 --> 00:41:20,019
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, vrlo je važno da danas gdje smo došli u ovoj župi,

1592
00:41:20,019 --> 00:41:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] što ova župa danas je, ne bi bila, ajmo reći,

1593
00:41:23,619 --> 00:41:26,320
[SPEAKER_01] bez one, možda, tri, četiri bakice koje su to izbolile.

1594
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:29,480
[SPEAKER_01] A bilo bih samo tri ili četiri, da bi ovdje sad bilo,

1595
00:41:29,480 --> 00:41:31,659
[SPEAKER_01] možda, stotinu ili više ljudi.

1596
00:41:31,659 --> 00:41:36,059
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, da je životni kontekst, znači, služitelj

1597
00:41:36,059 --> 00:41:39,380
[SPEAKER_01] ili poslužitelj, one koji ima karizmu, neku službu u crkvi,

1598
00:41:39,380 --> 00:41:41,639
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, svjesan svog životnog konteksta.

1599
00:41:41,639 --> 00:41:42,920
[SPEAKER_01] I tekako, cijelo vrijeme.

1600
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:47,199
[SPEAKER_01] Druga stvar je, dakle, kaže se detaljno izlaganje.

1601
00:41:47,199 --> 00:41:52,880
[SPEAKER_01] Što to znači? Dakle, da je katehiziran, da ga zanima.

1602
00:41:53,219 --> 00:41:55,099
[SPEAKER_01] Što to znači biti čitač?

1603
00:41:55,099 --> 00:41:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] I to što čita, da se interesira za taj tekst koji će pročitat.

1604
00:41:58,559 --> 00:42:04,320
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, da, recimo, ja isto, evo, moram znati što to znači biti svečaj

1605
00:42:04,320 --> 00:42:06,659
[SPEAKER_01] kako se priprema u novicijatu za redovništvo,

1606
00:42:06,659 --> 00:42:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] uči o povijest svoga reda, svoga utemeljitelja, tako dalje, tako dalje.

1607
00:42:10,579 --> 00:42:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, neko, znači, ovaj dio je znanje.

1608
00:42:12,539 --> 00:42:17,320
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, životni kontekst. Drugo je, dakle, obrazovati se s obzirom na to što činiš.

1609
00:42:17,320 --> 00:42:19,280
[SPEAKER_01] Koja je pozadina tvoje službe?

1610
00:42:19,579 --> 00:42:22,840
[SPEAKER_01] Koja je sve bio u toj službi i u Svetom pismu i tako dalje?

1611
00:42:23,679 --> 00:42:28,300
[SPEAKER_01] Treće, ovo je jako isto važno, ajmo reći povijestno-spacijska perspektiva.

1612
00:42:28,300 --> 00:42:29,699
[SPEAKER_01] Što to znači? Znak vremena.

1613
00:42:29,699 --> 00:42:33,679
[SPEAKER_01] Moram biti svjestan vremena u kojem ja sad čitam tu riječ,

1614
00:42:33,679 --> 00:42:37,119
[SPEAKER_01] navještam tu riječ, u kojem sam sakristan, u kojem sam svečanik,

1615
00:42:37,119 --> 00:42:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem sam, ne znam, bilo što što radim u crkvi.

1616
00:42:40,079 --> 00:42:41,820
[SPEAKER_01] Moram biti svjestan toga vremena.

1617
00:42:41,820 --> 00:42:44,360
[SPEAKER_01] A ne misliti da misle još uvijek na latinskom.

1618
00:42:44,360 --> 00:42:51,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ili da papa još uvijek nosi krunu, tijaru, jel?

1619
00:42:51,360 --> 00:42:54,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ili da, ne znam, svečnici još uvijek mogu ženiti.

1620
00:42:54,340 --> 00:42:55,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ili tako dalje, jel?

1621
00:42:55,699 --> 00:42:57,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, biti, karikiram bez veze,

1622
00:42:57,699 --> 00:43:00,260
[SPEAKER_01] uglavnom biti svjestan vremena u kojem jesam.

1623
00:43:00,260 --> 00:43:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] I četvrto, da one koji poslužuje u to svoje posluživanje

1624
00:43:05,480 --> 00:43:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] je uključio svoju osobnost.

1625
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] A ne jedno je na kavi, a drugo je tu sad na bonu

1626
00:43:11,699 --> 00:43:13,739
[SPEAKER_01] ili u crkvi i tako dalje, ili obrnuto, jel?

1627
00:43:13,739 --> 00:43:17,360
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, uključio je, ne znam, u svoje sakristanstvo,

1628
00:43:17,360 --> 00:43:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] u to svoje što svira, u svoje svečaništvo i tako dalje,

1629
00:43:20,380 --> 00:43:21,599
[SPEAKER_01] svoju osobnost.

1630
00:43:21,599 --> 00:43:24,039
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono što Pavao Timotevite kako kaže, jel?

1631
00:43:24,039 --> 00:43:25,639
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne to negirati.

1632
00:43:25,639 --> 00:43:28,320
[SPEAKER_01] S razlogom, te baš tako kakav jesi,

1633
00:43:28,699 --> 00:43:30,900
[SPEAKER_01] je Duh Sveti dao tu određenu karizmu.

1634
00:43:30,900 --> 00:43:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, da, jer očito ta karizma

1635
00:43:34,019 --> 00:43:36,400
[SPEAKER_01] odgovara to tvojoj osobnosti.

1636
00:43:36,400 --> 00:43:39,579
[SPEAKER_01] I tvoja osobnost odgovara toj tvojoj karizmi.

1637
00:43:39,579 --> 00:43:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] Evo.

1638
00:43:40,019 --> 00:43:42,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, to su ta četiri kriterija

1639
00:43:42,159 --> 00:43:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] s kojima sam htio zaključiti.

1640
00:43:43,960 --> 00:43:47,239
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ima li ko kako pitanje?

1641
00:43:47,239 --> 00:43:56,400
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, evo, trudnice imaju prednost.

1642
00:43:57,139 --> 00:43:59,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ali i žene.

1643
00:43:59,900 --> 00:44:02,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ima pitanje osobe koja sliša ovanju.

1644
00:44:02,920 --> 00:44:05,780
[UNKNOWN] Kako osvijestiti i saznati?

1645
00:44:05,780 --> 00:44:09,099
[SPEAKER_01] Kako osvijestiti i saznati?

1646
00:44:09,099 --> 00:44:10,519
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ovako.

1647
00:44:10,519 --> 00:44:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] Prije svega,

1648
00:44:11,739 --> 00:44:15,059
[SPEAKER_01] e da, to sam si isto zapisao.

1649
00:44:15,059 --> 00:44:17,159
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala osobi koja je na odlajnu.

1650
00:44:17,880 --> 00:44:21,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo bi sad totalno priskočio.

1651
00:44:21,239 --> 00:44:22,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ali zapisao sam si to.

1652
00:44:22,260 --> 00:44:23,400
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ovako.

1653
00:44:23,400 --> 00:44:24,440
[SPEAKER_01] Prije svega,

1654
00:44:24,440 --> 00:44:28,400
[SPEAKER_01] postoje ponavljanje,

1655
00:44:28,400 --> 00:44:30,199
[SPEAKER_01] čisto mali kontekst za ovo pitanje.

1656
00:44:30,199 --> 00:44:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, postoje nešto znamo ponavljanje

1657
00:44:31,900 --> 00:44:32,980
[SPEAKER_01] duhovskih znakova.

1658
00:44:32,980 --> 00:44:34,880
[SPEAKER_01] Duhovski znakovi su znakovi koji su bili na pedesetnici.

1659
00:44:34,880 --> 00:44:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, to je nešto što se tiče

1660
00:44:37,000 --> 00:44:38,599
[SPEAKER_01] svakog šlana crkve.

1661
00:44:39,159 --> 00:44:40,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ponavljanje duhovskih znakova se čini

1662
00:44:40,920 --> 00:44:42,719
[SPEAKER_01] kroz krštenje i polaganje ruku.

1663
00:44:42,719 --> 00:44:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Objasnio sam polaganje ruku.

1664
00:44:44,000 --> 00:44:45,059
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, vam reći,

1665
00:44:45,059 --> 00:44:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] zaraziti nekoga svojom karizmom.

1666
00:44:47,980 --> 00:44:49,440
[SPEAKER_01] Zaraziti u pozitivnom smislu.

1667
00:44:49,440 --> 00:44:52,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je na tu osobu neko položio ruke,

1668
00:44:52,500 --> 00:44:53,840
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1669
00:44:53,840 --> 00:44:57,199
[SPEAKER_01] važno je da ode kod svog oca svoje karizme.

1670
00:44:57,199 --> 00:44:58,260
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, tako nazvat.

1671
00:44:58,260 --> 00:45:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] Da sazna u koje karizme je taj

1672
00:45:01,980 --> 00:45:03,619
[SPEAKER_01] ko je položio ruku na nju imao.

1673
00:45:03,619 --> 00:45:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] I to je sigurno nešto što čeka i tu osobu.

1674
00:45:05,480 --> 00:45:08,019
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, da li ta karizma

1675
00:45:08,019 --> 00:45:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] odgovara toj osobi.

1676
00:45:09,960 --> 00:45:11,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ovdje sad postoji jedna opasnost.

1677
00:45:11,860 --> 00:45:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] A to je ovo.

1678
00:45:12,460 --> 00:45:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] Vi možete izmoliti karizmu

1679
00:45:14,579 --> 00:45:15,400
[SPEAKER_01] koju baš želite.

1680
00:45:15,400 --> 00:45:17,219
[SPEAKER_01] Baš želim prorokovati.

1681
00:45:17,219 --> 00:45:18,199
[SPEAKER_01] Baš želim prorokovati.

1682
00:45:18,199 --> 00:45:19,559
[SPEAKER_01] I možeš si to izmoliti,

1683
00:45:19,559 --> 00:45:22,980
[SPEAKER_01] ali čak i kako to nije Božja volja za tebe.

1684
00:45:22,980 --> 00:45:25,320
[SPEAKER_01] To je nešto što sam na Tereziji Javilskoj

1685
00:45:25,320 --> 00:45:26,659
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam ju citirao isto rekao.

1686
00:45:26,659 --> 00:45:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] To može, ako imaš određeni dar

1687
00:45:28,260 --> 00:45:29,219
[SPEAKER_01] koji si izmolio,

1688
00:45:29,219 --> 00:45:30,820
[SPEAKER_01] ne znači da je to automatski

1689
00:45:30,820 --> 00:45:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] bila Božja volja za tebe.

1690
00:45:32,019 --> 00:45:33,119
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1691
00:45:33,119 --> 00:45:35,639
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što Bog ti je to dao,

1692
00:45:35,780 --> 00:45:37,739
[SPEAKER_01] iako to nije htio za tebe,

1693
00:45:37,739 --> 00:45:39,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali dao ti je da shvatiš,

1694
00:45:39,039 --> 00:45:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] da te lupi po glavi,

1695
00:45:39,960 --> 00:45:41,360
[SPEAKER_01] da svremljeno shvatiš

1696
00:45:41,360 --> 00:45:42,760
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je to bio promašaj za tebe.

1697
00:45:42,760 --> 00:45:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sjetim se Tereziji Javilske,

1698
00:45:44,119 --> 00:45:45,840
[SPEAKER_01] citirao sam mu kad je rekla

1699
00:45:45,840 --> 00:45:47,360
[SPEAKER_01] da su joj više donijele

1700
00:45:47,360 --> 00:45:50,360
[SPEAKER_01] suza uslišane molitve.

1701
00:45:50,360 --> 00:45:51,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da je više zaplakala

1702
00:45:51,320 --> 00:45:52,599
[SPEAKER_01] zbog uslišanih molitava.

1703
00:45:53,440 --> 00:45:55,340
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, samo da je u nauči pameti Bog.

1704
00:45:55,340 --> 00:45:56,280
[SPEAKER_01] Tako i ovdje.

1705
00:45:56,280 --> 00:45:56,940
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1706
00:45:56,940 --> 00:45:59,559
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto nije dobro izmoliti karizmu?

1707
00:45:59,559 --> 00:46:02,199
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što će doći do oholosti,

1708
00:46:02,199 --> 00:46:03,719
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam zaslužao za to.

1709
00:46:03,719 --> 00:46:05,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam si to izmolio

1710
00:46:05,179 --> 00:46:07,579
[SPEAKER_01] i moja duhovna, ne znam,

1711
00:46:07,579 --> 00:46:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] struktura je bila toliko jaka

1712
00:46:09,500 --> 00:46:10,679
[SPEAKER_01] da si ja to izmolio.

1713
00:46:10,679 --> 00:46:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] I onda nemaš tu percepciju,

1714
00:46:11,699 --> 00:46:12,199
[SPEAKER_01] je to dar.

1715
00:46:12,199 --> 00:46:14,920
[SPEAKER_01] Nego si si ti to izmolio,

1716
00:46:14,920 --> 00:46:16,019
[SPEAKER_01] ti si to zaslužio.

1717
00:46:16,019 --> 00:46:17,840
[SPEAKER_01] Kada nije izmoljeno,

1718
00:46:17,840 --> 00:46:19,199
[SPEAKER_01] nego je zaista darovano,

1719
00:46:19,199 --> 00:46:21,739
[SPEAKER_01] e, onda je mogućnost puno poniznija.

1720
00:46:21,820 --> 00:46:22,980
[SPEAKER_01] A po čemu ćemo to znati?

1721
00:46:22,980 --> 00:46:24,840
[SPEAKER_01] U ovom energomata.

1722
00:46:24,840 --> 00:46:27,239
[SPEAKER_01] Pusti, ako osoba već ima neku karizmu,

1723
00:46:27,239 --> 00:46:29,559
[SPEAKER_01] a nije sigurno li je karizma ili nije,

1724
00:46:29,559 --> 00:46:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] ako misli da je ta karizma,

1725
00:46:31,039 --> 00:46:32,260
[SPEAKER_01] neko i dalje živi.

1726
00:46:32,260 --> 00:46:34,360
[SPEAKER_01] A moraju proći kroz ovo diakonija,

1727
00:46:34,360 --> 00:46:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] dakle kroz služenje.

1728
00:46:35,539 --> 00:46:37,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ju tjera na služenje,

1729
00:46:37,699 --> 00:46:38,780
[SPEAKER_01] to je autentično.

1730
00:46:38,780 --> 00:46:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ju tjera na služenje.

1731
00:46:40,019 --> 00:46:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] I ako u djelovanju energomata,

1732
00:46:42,960 --> 00:46:44,280
[SPEAKER_01] sveti Pavao kaže,

1733
00:46:44,280 --> 00:46:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] se vidi jedan od ploda duha svetoga.

1734
00:46:49,519 --> 00:46:51,420
[SPEAKER_01] Vi znate koji su plodovi duha svetoga.

1735
00:46:51,820 --> 00:46:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] Pavao ih, dakle, na braja.

1736
00:46:53,300 --> 00:46:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] Moram ih ja zapisati.

1737
00:46:54,739 --> 00:46:56,679
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, jel, u Galačini ima pet.

1738
00:46:56,679 --> 00:46:58,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ljubav, znači ako ona u djelovanju

1739
00:46:58,820 --> 00:47:00,380
[SPEAKER_01] osjeća zbog te karizme,

1740
00:47:00,380 --> 00:47:02,980
[SPEAKER_01] ljubav, radost, mir, velikodušnost,

1741
00:47:02,980 --> 00:47:04,880
[SPEAKER_01] uslužnost, dobrotu, vjernost, blagost,

1742
00:47:04,880 --> 00:47:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] uzdrživost.

1743
00:47:05,940 --> 00:47:07,820
[SPEAKER_01] ili, kako bi danas rekli, samokontrola.

1744
00:47:07,820 --> 00:47:08,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ok?

1745
00:47:08,440 --> 00:47:10,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ode je karizma autentična.

1746
00:47:10,440 --> 00:47:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, ako si u nekoj dubiozi,

1747
00:47:13,000 --> 00:47:15,619
[SPEAKER_01] da li imaš tu karizmu neku,

1748
00:47:15,619 --> 00:47:17,239
[SPEAKER_01] uzmi ju, kao da ju imaš.

1749
00:47:17,239 --> 00:47:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je moj savjet.

1750
00:47:18,000 --> 00:47:18,960
[SPEAKER_01] Uzmi ju, kao da ju imaš.

1751
00:47:18,960 --> 00:47:20,579
[SPEAKER_01] A vrijeme će pokazati,

1752
00:47:20,579 --> 00:47:23,219
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, da li je tvoja karizma dodjela

1753
00:47:23,219 --> 00:47:24,739
[SPEAKER_01] ove plodove, ove plodove duha.

1754
00:47:24,860 --> 00:47:26,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ne, idemo dalje.

1755
00:47:26,659 --> 00:47:29,440
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi ste shvatili?

1756
00:47:29,440 --> 00:47:30,800
[SPEAKER_01] Dalje.

1757
00:47:30,800 --> 00:47:33,300
[SPEAKER_01] S određenom da sam spomenuo

1758
00:47:33,300 --> 00:47:35,159
[UNKNOWN] da nam tog svega je te djelovanje,

1759
00:47:35,159 --> 00:47:36,880
[UNKNOWN] a da djelovanje ne postoje,

1760
00:47:36,880 --> 00:47:38,659
[UNKNOWN] da je to kuma djelovanje mučaništva.

1761
00:47:38,659 --> 00:47:41,179
[SPEAKER_01] Za određenu karizmu.

1762
00:47:41,179 --> 00:47:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] Za karizmu postojanosti, celibata, vjernosti.

1763
00:47:45,079 --> 00:47:47,719
[SPEAKER_01] Jest, znači, to, Eder.

1764
00:47:47,719 --> 00:47:49,940
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, za tu karizmu, da, mučaništvo.

1765
00:47:49,940 --> 00:47:51,440
[SPEAKER_01] Zatim, recimo, s određenom da je

1766
00:47:51,440 --> 00:47:53,539
[UNKNOWN] Anovići Isuska stavlja mučaništva

1767
00:47:53,539 --> 00:47:55,380
[UNKNOWN] i Anovići Isuska stavlja mučaništva.

1768
00:47:55,380 --> 00:47:56,019
[UNKNOWN] Znači, recimo, djelovat,

1769
00:47:56,019 --> 00:47:57,960
[UNKNOWN] da nam to tako nazvat, politički,

1770
00:47:57,960 --> 00:47:59,380
[UNKNOWN] a neki način ove reko-kerodu,

1771
00:47:59,380 --> 00:48:01,739
[UNKNOWN] tada će u Benković, ove reko, ne znam,

1772
00:48:01,739 --> 00:48:02,599
[UNKNOWN] ne znam, ne znam, ne znam, ne znam,

1773
00:48:02,599 --> 00:48:03,739
[UNKNOWN] a ne znam, ne znam, ne znam, ne znam,

1774
00:48:03,739 --> 00:48:04,820
[UNKNOWN] ne znam, ne znam, ne znam, ne znam, ne znam,

1775
00:48:04,820 --> 00:48:05,679
[UNKNOWN] ne znam, ne znam, ne znam, ne znam, ne znam, ne znam,

1776
00:48:05,679 --> 00:48:07,480
[UNKNOWN] da za nas kršeno je to djelovanje

1777
00:48:07,480 --> 00:48:09,139
[UNKNOWN] smjereno na taj društveni politički,

1778
00:48:09,139 --> 00:48:12,280
[UNKNOWN] učinu, kako viđamo sad da koruncija lažnih prebari,

1779
00:48:12,280 --> 00:48:14,599
[UNKNOWN] ili to je ovaj trafik uzmero na ide.

1780
00:48:14,599 --> 00:48:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] Samo.

1781
00:48:16,079 --> 00:48:22,820
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sjetite se kada sam radio ovo u ovoj pneumatici,

1782
00:48:22,820 --> 00:48:27,239
[SPEAKER_01] znači, prorokovanje je dar za onoga koji to može raditi.

1783
00:48:27,239 --> 00:48:29,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ako imaš karizmu biti prorok,

1784
00:48:29,179 --> 00:48:31,360
[SPEAKER_01] onda si pozvan prozivati,

1785
00:48:31,360 --> 00:48:32,920
[SPEAKER_01] a to su Ivan Krasitelji i Isus bili,

1786
00:48:32,920 --> 00:48:35,059
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, prozivati, utemeljiti,

1787
00:48:35,059 --> 00:48:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] čistiti zajednicu, društveni poredak i tako dalje.

1788
00:48:38,039 --> 00:48:41,099
[SPEAKER_01] Neko ko ima karizmu prorokovanja, da,

1789
00:48:41,099 --> 00:48:43,320
[SPEAKER_01] ali samo ko ima karizmu prorokovanja.

1790
00:48:44,519 --> 00:48:46,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ok? Znači, rekli smo,

1791
00:48:46,699 --> 00:48:48,139
[SPEAKER_01] karizma je prorokovanje,

1792
00:48:48,139 --> 00:48:50,280
[SPEAKER_01] diakonija je tumačenje,

1793
00:48:50,280 --> 00:48:53,639
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno, razlučivanje duhova od prorokovanja,

1794
00:48:53,639 --> 00:48:56,179
[SPEAKER_01] a energobata djelovanje od prorokovanja

1795
00:48:56,179 --> 00:48:57,480
[SPEAKER_01] je, dakle,

1796
00:48:57,480 --> 00:49:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] kad prođeš razlučivanje duhova,

1797
00:49:00,480 --> 00:49:01,639
[SPEAKER_01] je, dakle, upravo to.

1798
00:49:01,639 --> 00:49:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, baš to, staviti, jer vidite,

1799
00:49:04,559 --> 00:49:06,800
[SPEAKER_01] zato sam dao ovaj prvi primjer

1800
00:49:06,800 --> 00:49:08,880
[SPEAKER_01] u ovaj knjizi izlaska.

1801
00:49:08,880 --> 00:49:10,480
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko je karizma prorokovanja,

1802
00:49:10,480 --> 00:49:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, povezana sa utemeljenjem,

1803
00:49:13,860 --> 00:49:15,679
[SPEAKER_01] sudsko pravno poredka,

1804
00:49:15,679 --> 00:49:17,280
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, u izrazanskoj zajednici,

1805
00:49:17,280 --> 00:49:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] itd., itd., jel?

1806
00:49:18,539 --> 00:49:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] E.

1807
00:49:19,000 --> 00:49:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] Dalje.

1808
00:49:26,079 --> 00:49:27,500
[UNKNOWN] Tiče karizme lječenja,

1809
00:49:27,500 --> 00:49:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] imamo primjer da se, recimo,

1810
00:49:30,539 --> 00:49:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] čak isti služitelji u Africi,

1811
00:49:32,699 --> 00:49:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] Južnoj Americi, baš autentično,

1812
00:49:34,739 --> 00:49:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] medicinski potvrđeno,

1813
00:49:35,960 --> 00:49:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] se događa velik broj,

1814
00:49:37,539 --> 00:49:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] tu nema, recimo, na zapadu,

1815
00:49:40,280 --> 00:49:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] kod nas nema, jako.

1816
00:49:41,880 --> 00:49:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji su možda uzorci tobe,

1817
00:49:43,420 --> 00:49:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] baš karizma lječenja,

1818
00:49:44,920 --> 00:49:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] još u našim krajem,

1819
00:49:46,699 --> 00:49:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] ok, što inemo zapadnije,

1820
00:49:48,119 --> 00:49:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] to teže,

1821
00:49:48,739 --> 00:49:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] to je do ozdravljenja.

1822
00:49:50,219 --> 00:49:51,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako, rekli smo, znači,

1823
00:49:51,280 --> 00:49:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] kod karizme lječenja,

1824
00:49:53,300 --> 00:49:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] znači, prolazi se kroz služenje

1825
00:49:55,199 --> 00:49:56,739
[SPEAKER_01] diakoniju, to što čudotvorstva,

1826
00:49:56,739 --> 00:49:58,480
[SPEAKER_01] i energomata je posvećivanje,

1827
00:49:58,480 --> 00:49:59,980
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, spašavanje duša,

1828
00:49:59,980 --> 00:50:01,699
[SPEAKER_01] u institucionalnom smislu

1829
00:50:01,699 --> 00:50:03,199
[SPEAKER_01] sakramenti, egzorcizama, itd.

1830
00:50:03,199 --> 00:50:05,219
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, zato što je energomata

1831
00:50:05,219 --> 00:50:06,420
[SPEAKER_01] na zapadu, dakle,

1832
00:50:06,420 --> 00:50:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] sakramenti je ovo ono,

1833
00:50:07,380 --> 00:50:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] izgubila svoju karizmu.

1834
00:50:08,500 --> 00:50:10,380
[SPEAKER_01] Izgubila je svoju karizmu.

1835
00:50:10,380 --> 00:50:12,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, mi danas dijelimo sakramente

1836
00:50:12,679 --> 00:50:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] na zapadu, govorim,

1837
00:50:13,699 --> 00:50:15,139
[SPEAKER_01] dijelimo sakramente

1838
00:50:15,139 --> 00:50:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] bez, dakle, tog karizmatsko,

1839
00:50:17,119 --> 00:50:18,699
[SPEAKER_01] kao bisire pred svinje, jel?

1840
00:50:18,699 --> 00:50:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, bez otvorenosti karizmi

1841
00:50:21,099 --> 00:50:22,880
[SPEAKER_01] koju određeni sakrament daje.

1842
00:50:22,880 --> 00:50:24,900
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, opet čašćivanje,

1843
00:50:24,900 --> 00:50:26,820
[SPEAKER_01] pričašćivanja rastavljenih,

1844
00:50:26,820 --> 00:50:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] opet oželjenih, jel?

1845
00:50:28,420 --> 00:50:29,840
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto što te, ono,

1846
00:50:29,840 --> 00:50:32,619
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, to, znači, totalno, evo,

1847
00:50:32,619 --> 00:50:34,320
[SPEAKER_01] posvećivanje je izgubilo

1848
00:50:34,320 --> 00:50:35,360
[SPEAKER_01] svoju vrijednost.

1849
00:50:35,360 --> 00:50:36,400
[SPEAKER_01] Više nije posvećivanje,

1850
00:50:36,400 --> 00:50:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] nego je, evo, vidite,

1851
00:50:38,960 --> 00:50:40,159
[SPEAKER_01] znači, energomata je izgubila

1852
00:50:40,159 --> 00:50:41,519
[SPEAKER_01] svoju karizmata, jel?

1853
00:50:41,519 --> 00:50:42,639
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, posvećivanje je izgubilo

1854
00:50:42,639 --> 00:50:44,539
[SPEAKER_01] ovo, dar liječenja, jel?

1855
00:50:44,539 --> 00:50:45,599
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, u tome je stvar.

1856
00:50:45,599 --> 00:50:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da je posvećivanje izgubilo

1857
00:50:47,000 --> 00:50:48,480
[SPEAKER_01] dar liječenja, ne da se dar,

1858
00:50:48,480 --> 00:50:49,900
[SPEAKER_01] da je dar liječenja izgubio

1859
00:50:49,900 --> 00:50:51,519
